{"tid":2277020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田 50歲男 源頭不明個案","createTime":"2020-11-08T07:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T07:58:25.000Z","uid":64603,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"149542d04fb50ea405c0230c1103328225045cd4","tid":2277020,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0kaisp9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0kaisp9.jpg&h=f863a853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港今日（8日）錄得10宗武漢肺炎確診個案，包括昨日（7日）公佈的3宗源頭不明初步確診個案，今日證實確診，當中包括一名50歲男子（第5375號個案），其妻子在沙田聖公會主風小學任教師；另有7宗輸入個案，衞生署下午將不會召開疫情記者會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/GRH5GSP4XJA37DGG2VVYEG54UU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FGRH5GSP4XJA37DGG2VVYEG54UU%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=10b5c62b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FGRH5GSP4XJA37DGG2VVYEG54UU%2F&h=aef0bd8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/GRH5GSP4XJA37DGG2VVYEG54UU/</a>"},{"pid":"1eb3a52d9baf366055ada826182db3f8c5b88e39","tid":2277020,"uid":76804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"呢兩日全部都係男人<br />\n明架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47351765ecea77eb200c7157ec9a12a88133b40c","tid":2277020,"uid":81756,"like":3,"dislik